title: Fix Null pointer exception on Settings
message:
Fix Null pointer exception on Settings

First on old devices the call to bindPreferenceSummaryToValue was using a non existing preference key leading to a null pointer exception on these devices.
Potentially onWindowFocusChanged could be called with an uninitialized mRespiStateManager.

title: Add appcompat library to the project

Add appcompat library to the project

actionbar has disappeared from the settings page.

build (android studio):
